{"tid":1828823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"如果香港大地震...你會...","createTime":"2020-01-18T07:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T09:15:10.000Z","uid":266362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dbf5a45124eba836dacd7b4bc5911ba917450501","tid":1828823,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:53:34.000Z","msg":"尋日有人影到 50-100條殺人鯨/偽虎鯨現身於維港水域，又想到12月5日及1月5日分別發生香港微震，再諗到「大自然地震預警」地震魚/皇帶魚，難免令人聯想到係咪香港大地震既先兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iKpgT95.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiKpgT95.png&h=f209ed4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影片：<a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/1FVRQc3ZJYcEsMhg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F1FVRQc3ZJYcEsMhg&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=f91696a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/1FVRQc3ZJYcEsMhg</a><br />\n<br />\n之後我上網搵False killer whales 殺人鯨/偽虎鯨 VS Oarfish 皇帶魚(地震魚)住幾深... 點知發現殺人鯨/偽虎鯨住響仲深過地震魚既海域<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係有可能係香港大地震先兆？<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n殺人鯨/偽虎鯨<br />\n<br />\nFalse killer whales are expert divers and prefer living in deep waters around 15,420 feet (4,700 m) deep.<br />\n<br />\n1) 擅於潛水<br />\n2) 住在深海 4700米<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n皇帶魚/地震魚<br />\n<br />\nAdult oarfish are thought to live solitary lives. Oarfish are a pelagic species found throughout the deep seas of the eastern Atlantic Ocean and Mediterranean Sea. They are usually found at a depth of around 600 feet (200 meters), although they have been known to go as deep as 3,000 feet (1,000 meters).<br />\n<br />\n1) 多數響水深 200米找到地震魚<br />\n2) 佢地可以深潛到 1000 米<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">如果真係有香港大地震，大家會點求生？又或者會做咩？集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />互相提點求生</span></span>"},{"pid":"e10287bd377274e957ef3f1b5666bd3cc2d93fcf","tid":1828823,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:54:22.000Z","msg":"P仔自推x1"},{"pid":"a1472bc8b0f1fc08fc35625a3c778ce5cc3bb500","tid":1828823,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:54:34.000Z","msg":"P仔自推x2"},{"pid":"dc8b2aaf14ca3ec9bf6789cd4625234ad0b57d68","tid":1828823,"uid":52942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:54:47.000Z","msg":"香港d樓咁密，食住花生等睇骨牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdd46c80b5c984eba84644d3af287c1bd60f97d","tid":1828823,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:54:48.000Z","msg":"P仔自推x3"},{"pid":"a27ce5ac0b0983756b02b556649888f7cfd04568","tid":1828823,"uid":248960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:54:56.000Z","msg":"等死"},{"pid":"802f6e7377946cf860f2bd3bb07bd29e2d273971","tid":1828823,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco